```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant SSG as LessJS SSG
    participant DH as DocsHome (Lit)
    participant Layout as less-layout
    participant Islands as Island Components

    Browser->>SSG: GET /
    SSG->>DH: DSD render()
    DH->>Layout: render <less-layout>

    Note over DH: v8 区块渲染（新顺序）

    DH->>DH: ① Hero（精简：无 stat/term-demo<br/>h1: "全栈框架 · 零 JS 首屏 · 多框架共存"<br/>desc: 单行短句）

    rect rgb(17, 17, 39)
        Note right of DH: 暗色连续（无分割线）
        DH->>DH: ② Code Strip（不变）
    end

    Note over DH: section-transition--flip<br/>品牌色渐变线 暗→浅翻转

    rect rgb(255, 255, 255)
        Note right of DH: 浅色叙事区
        DH->>DH: ③ Benchmark<br/>+ bench-stats (从 Hero 搬来 4 个 stat)<br/>+ astro-callout (Astro 对比说明)
        DH->>DH: ④ Multi-framework<br/>(去掉 sec-lbl，保留 sec-title)<br/><less-showcase-panel>
    end

    Note over DH: section-transition--glow<br/>品牌色光晕分割

    DH->>DH: ⑤ Bento Grid<br/>WC Engine 主导全宽卡 + pills<br/>F + I 并排辅助卡

    Note over DH: section-transition--warm<br/>渐变过渡 浅→暖灰

    DH->>DH: ⑥ Quick Start<br/>每步 +qs-desc 说明文字<br/>底部 +qs-cta 按钮

    DH->>DH: Footer（暖灰 #F1EFE8，不变）

    DH-->>SSG: DSD HTML
    SSG-->>Browser: 零 JS 首屏（完整 HTML）

    Browser->>Islands: hydrate island components
    activate Islands
    Islands-->>Browser: less-showcase-panel 可交互
    Islands-->>Browser: less-search 可交互
    deactivate Islands
```
